title: Importance of Questioning Data
text: The quality of the questions you ask will guide you to meaningful insights in your analysis and allow you to dive deeper into the significance.

title: Understanding Data Insights
text: Accepting the first data insight during data analysis may not be the best idea since it may be misleading, or other insights might be more valuable to the specific task at hand.

title: Knowing the Purpose of the Data Analysis
text: The most interesting finding about your data may not necessarily be what points to the implications of the data.
